art of the family he is being fostered by. But they also take him closer to the day that he is due to leave them forever… </p><p>Send your imagination into orbit and read the first chapter here!</p><p>Also check out our Frank Cottrell Boyce <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/gallery/2016/apr/04/frank-cottrell-boyce-scrapbook-sputniks-guide-to-life\">Sputnik gallery</a> and <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2016/apr/04/frank-cottrell-boyce-sputnik-guide-to-life-on-earth-competition\">competition</a> </p>","body":"<figure class=\"element element-embed\" data-alt=\"Sputnik's Guide to Life on Earth\">  <iframe class=\"scribd_iframe_embed\" src=\"https://www.scribd.com/embeds/305196466/content?start_page=1&view_mode=slideshow&access_key=key-IPqImAswCjBlEisTY69v&show_recommendations=false\" data-auto-height=\"false\" data-aspect-ratio=\"0.6595900439238653\" scrolling=\"no\" id=\"doc_77995\" width=\"100%\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> </figure>","productionOffice":"UK","trailText":"Send your imagination into orbit and read the first chapter of the new book by award-winning author Frank Cottrell-Boyce here!","headline":"Free read! Sputnik's Guide to Life on Earth by Frank Cottrell Boyce and Steve Lenton"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/ng-interactive/2016/apr/04/extract-sputniks-guide-to-life-on-earth-by-frank-cottrell-boyce-and-steve-lenton","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/childrens-books-site/ng-interactive/2016/apr/04/extract-sputniks-guide-to-life-on-earth-by-frank-cottrell-boyce-and-steve-lenton","sectionName":"Children's books","elements":[{"id":"5b6b52b4ff6047dadfdc222360cf64dcacbe5b5c","relation":"thumbnail","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/5b6b52b4ff6047dadfdc222360cf64dcacbe5b5c/209_0_1185_711/1000.jpg","typeData":{"mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/5b6b52b4ff6047dadfdc222360cf64dcacbe5b5c","altText":"Sputnik'