ons on the way. Later this year sees the release of Cell, with John Cusack and Samuel L Jackson while It and The Dark Tower, starring Idris Elba and Matthew McConaughey are also heading towards production.</p> <p>King has confessed that he’s not a fan of Stanley Kubrick’s take on The Shining. Last year, he spoke to <a href=\"http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/features/stephen-king-the-rolling-stone-interview-20141031?page=5\">Rolling Stone</a> and called the movie “misogynistic” for presenting Wendy Torrance as “a screaming dishrag”. He was also involved in a TV miniseries based on the same book, starring Steven Weber and Rebecca de Mornay.</p>","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/4t4xc","wordcount":"220","thumbnail":"http://media.guim.co.uk/75684fefd0c38e028b255853f1cc8d035b77d024/0_0_2994_1796/500.jpg","commentCloseDate":"2016-04-07T09:00:00Z","standfirst":"<p>The script for Doctor Sleep, which follows a traumatised middle-aged Danny, is to be written by Oscar-winner Akiva Goldsman</p>"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/apr/04/stephen-king-shining-sequel-adaptation","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/2016/apr/04/stephen-king-shining-sequel-adaptation","sectionName":"Film","elements":[{"id":"75684fefd0c38e028b255853f1cc8d035b77d024","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/75684fefd0c38e028b255853f1cc8d035b77d024/0_0_2994_1796/2000.jpg","typeData":{"mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/75684fefd0c38e028b255853f1cc8d035b77d024","suppliersReference":"NYET409","altText":"Shine on ... Stephen King will exec produce the adaptation of Doctor Sleep.","caption":"Shine on ... Stephen King will exec produce the adaptation of Doctor Sleep.","photographer":"Francois Mori","source":"AP","credit":"Photograph: Francois Mori/AP","mediaId":"75684fefd0c38e028b255853f1cc8d035b77d024","displayCredit":"true","imageType":"Photograph","secureFile":"https://media.guim.co.uk/75684fefd0c38e028b255853f1cc8d0